    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>honey</strong>,<strong> soy sauce</strong>,<strong> chilli flakes </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!)<strong> </strong>and a pinch of<strong> sugar </strong>to the measuring jug and stir it all together – this is your <strong>Szechuan-style sauce</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>Szechuan-style sauce </strong>to the pan and bring to the boil</p><p>Once boiling, cook for 1-2 minutes or until thickened</p>",
